    <published>2016-02-04T09:54:01.000Z</published>
    <updated>2016-02-04T12:23:23.789Z</updated>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="u5185_u5BB9_u63D0_u8981"><a href="#u5185_u5BB9_u63D0_u8981" class="headerlink" title="内容提要"></a>内容提要</h3><blockquote>
<ul>
<li>注册github,创建github page</li>
<li>git，node.js，hexo的安装</li>
<li>域名的购买与解析</li>
<li>hexo的基础用法<a id="more"></a>
</li>
</ul>
</blockquote>
<hr>
<h3 id="Github_u7BC7"><a href="#Github_u7BC7" class="headerlink" title="Github篇"></a>Github篇</h3><h4 id="u6CE8_u518C"><a href="#u6CE8_u518C" class="headerlink" title="注册"></a>注册</h4><p>进<a href="https://github.com/" target="_blank" rel="external">官网</a>注册，并完成<a href="https://guides.github.com/activities/hello-world/" target="_blank" rel="external">教程</a>，掌握Repositories, Branches, Commits, Issues 和 Pull Requests的概念与用法.</p>
<h4 id="u521B_u5EFAgithub_page"><a href="#u521B_u5EFAgithub_page" class="headerlink" title="创建github page"></a>创建github page</h4><p>参考<a href="https://pages.github.com/" target="_blank" rel="external">pages主页</a></p>
<hr>
<h3 id="u5DE5_u5177_u51C6_u5907_u7BC7"><a href="#u5DE5_u5177_u51C6_u5907_u7BC7" class="headerlink" title="工具准备篇"></a>工具准备篇</h3><ol>
<li><a href="https://git-scm.com/" target="_blank" rel="external">git</a></li>
<li><a href="https://git-scm.com/" target="_blank" rel="external">node.js</a></li>
<li>hexo<br>使用git <code>$ npm install -g hexo</code></li>
</ol>
<hr>
<h3 id="u57DF_u540D_u7BC7"><a href="#u57DF_u540D_u7BC7" class="headerlink" title="域名篇"></a>域名篇</h3><p>可以使用阿里云的解决方案</p>
<blockquote>
<p><a href="http://wanwang.aliyun.com/" target="_blank" rel="external">域名购买</a><br><a href="https://help.aliyun.com/document_detail/dns/quick-start/hichina.html?spm=5176.776555913.6.98.S0rinO" target="_blank" rel="external">DNS设置</a>.</p>
</blockquote>
<hr>
<h3 id="hexo_u7BC7"><a href="#hexo_u7BC7" class="headerlink" title="hexo篇"></a>hexo篇</h3><p>Create a new post</p>
<blockquote>
<p>$ hexo new “My New Post”</p>
</blockquote>
<p>Run server</p>
<blockquote>
<p>$ hexo server</p>
</blockquote>
<p>Generate static files</p>
<blockquote>
<p>$ hexo generate</p>
</blockquote>
<p>Deploy to remote sites</p>
<blockquote>
<p>$ hexo deploy</p>
</blockquote>
<p>More info: <a href="http://hexo.io/docs/" target="_blank" rel="external">hexo docs</a></p>
]]></content>
